==English==
===Proper noun===
'''Juliet'''

#A female [[given name]].
#One of the [[main character]]s of [[w:William Shakespeare|William Shakespeare]]'s play ''[[w:Romeo and Juliet|Romeo and Juliet]]''.
#A woman who is or is with a great lover.
#A woman who is in love with a man from a family or party opposing that of her own.
#The sixth [[moon]] of the [[planet]] [[Uranus]].

